ANTHRAX - ARMENIA (02): (GEGHARKUNIK) CATTLE, HUMAN, OIE
********************************************************
A ProMED-mail post
http://www.promedmail.org
ProMED-mail is a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
http://www.isid.org

[1]
Date: Thu 22 Aug 2019
Source: ArmenPress [edited]
https://armenpress.am/eng/news/985614.html


Another 3 people in a small village in Gegharkunik province have been tested positive for anthrax, bringing the total number of confirmed cases to 8, the healthcare ministry said in a news release. The patients are receiving treatment and are recovering.

Preventive actions are being taken in the area.

On [Tue 20 Aug 2019], the Ministry of Healthcare reported that 5 people in Geghhovit village had contracted skin anthrax.

[byline: Stepan Kocharyan]

